3 Section 2. The requirements of subsection (7) of Section 1 of this Act shall only
4 apply to members serving on waste management district boards in counties containing
5 consolidated local governments, and any member who has exceeded the limitation on the
6 number of days that a member may serve after the expiration of his or her term on a
7 board of directors for a county containing a consolidated local government prior to the
8 effective date of this Act shall immediately vacate his or her seat.
9 Section 3. This Act takes effect January 6, 2026.
